import { Button, Divider, Flex, Text } from "@aws-amplify/ui-react";
import MyIcon from "./MyIcon";
export default function ActionCard(props) {
  const {
    debt = "$1.878.565.156",

                  height="19px"
                  gap="unset"

                  top="2px"
